00:24:48.905 --> 00:24:51.025
THE RESULT WILL BE ANNOUNCED TOMORROW

00:25:05.225 --> 00:25:07.745
TRANSFER COMPLETE
100,000 BAHT

00:25:35.905 --> 00:25:37.265
Suea, aren't you going to school?

00:25:38.665 --> 00:25:40.185
Yeah, Mom. I'll go soon.

00:25:40.265 --> 00:25:41.425
I'M SO EXCITED

00:25:41.505 --> 00:25:42.745
I CAN'T WAIT

00:25:42.825 --> 00:25:45.225
At this moment,
I would like to take this opportunity

00:25:45.305 --> 00:25:50.385
to allow Nanno to use this stage
to declare her bodily freedom.

00:25:56.945 --> 00:26:00.505
Thank you to everyone
who made today possible.

00:26:01.345 --> 00:26:05.105
I can't believe that my body

00:26:05.625 --> 00:26:08.505
could create so many miracles.

00:26:10.345 --> 00:26:12.465
But for me to get here today,

00:26:13.185 --> 00:26:15.545
there is one person
I must thank above all.

00:26:16.705 --> 00:26:18.345
And that person is

00:26:18.425 --> 00:26:19.545
Blossom.

00:26:25.905 --> 00:26:28.585
If Blossom hadn't inspired me

00:26:29.105 --> 00:26:33.545
and said that
our bodies should belong to us,

00:26:34.305 --> 00:26:36.745
we probably wouldn't be having
this much fun today.

00:26:38.745 --> 00:26:40.825
Thank you very much, Blossom.

00:26:48.705 --> 00:26:52.065
All right, let's find out

00:26:52.585 --> 00:26:54.625
who donated the most

00:26:55.185 --> 00:26:57.385
and will receive

00:26:58.305 --> 00:27:00.425
a one-night stand with me.

00:27:03.265 --> 00:27:05.465
I won't announce their name.

00:27:05.985 --> 00:27:09.345
Instead, I will announce the number.

00:27:12.745 --> 00:27:14.665
And the number

00:27:15.905 --> 00:27:17.425
is…

00:27:20.545 --> 00:27:21.705
one…

00:27:27.985 --> 00:27:29.465
zero…

00:27:33.305 --> 00:27:34.265
nine.

00:27:37.665 --> 00:27:38.825
Damn it!

00:27:40.385 --> 00:27:42.665
Number 109.

00:27:42.745 --> 00:27:46.345
Meet me at The Royal Resort Park Hotel,

00:27:47.385 --> 00:27:50.865
room 205.

00:27:52.385 --> 00:27:53.865
At 8:00 p.m.

00:27:56.985 --> 00:27:58.865
See you there.

00:27:58.945 --> 00:28:00.305
I'll be waiting.

00:28:08.825 --> 00:28:10.505
WHO'S 109?

00:28:10.585 --> 00:28:11.985
NOT ME

00:28:12.785 --> 00:28:15.305
Did she cheat again?

00:28:15.385 --> 00:28:17.185
WITH THIS MUCH MONEY,
OF COURSE I WOULDN'T WIN

00:28:17.265 --> 00:28:18.945
WHO THE HELL IS HE? HE'S LOADED.

00:28:34.225 --> 00:28:39.625
109 GETTING HER ALL TO HIMSELF ISN'T FAIR.
EVERYONE SHOULD GET SOMETHING.

00:28:47.745 --> 00:28:48.865
TRUE. WE ALSO DONATED A LOT.

00:28:48.945 --> 00:28:50.985
BITCH. GIVE ME MY MONEY BACK.

00:28:57.185 --> 00:28:58.105
Where are you going?

00:28:58.185 --> 00:28:59.385
You can't go in!

00:28:59.465 --> 00:29:02.345
-You can't go in!
-Wait!

00:29:02.425 --> 00:29:05.105
-If you're not a guest, you can't go in.
-We are the guests.

00:29:05.185 --> 00:29:06.585
Room 205.

00:29:06.665 --> 00:29:08.385
-Yeah, that's right.
-Yeah.

00:29:08.465 --> 00:29:10.905
-There are too many of you.
-I told you we're the guests.

00:29:26.105 --> 00:29:29.345
Damn it. Number 109,
you can't keep Nanno all to yourself.

00:29:29.425 --> 00:29:31.465
Damn it. Let me see your face.

00:29:31.985 --> 00:29:33.385
-What the hell?
-Shit.

00:29:43.945 --> 00:29:46.985
The person who donated the most
to the education fund

00:29:48.585 --> 00:29:52.265
will get a one-night stand with me.

00:29:53.145 --> 00:29:55.345
274,600 BAHT
CONFIRM TRANSACTION

00:29:58.745 --> 00:30:00.905
Number 109.

00:30:04.905 --> 00:30:06.785
You used your money
to do something like this?

00:30:06.865 --> 00:30:07.985
Get down here!

00:30:08.065 --> 00:30:10.105
Drag him down! Beat him up!

00:30:18.585 --> 00:30:21.665
Calm down. What's going on here?

00:30:23.585 --> 00:30:25.225
She's telling us to calm down.

00:30:28.225 --> 00:30:30.305
How the hell are we supposed to stay calm?

00:30:30.825 --> 00:30:33.265
We spent so much money on you.

00:30:33.865 --> 00:30:35.625
And we didn't get anything at all.

00:30:36.505 --> 00:30:38.745
But everything went
according to the rules.

00:30:39.265 --> 00:30:41.065
What rules?

00:30:43.105 --> 00:30:46.585
Me and the OnlyNanno fans,

00:30:47.105 --> 00:30:48.545
we paid you so much money.

00:30:48.625 --> 00:30:52.385
But that old bastard lying over there
gets you all to himself.

00:30:52.985 --> 00:30:54.425
That's not fair.

00:30:55.465 --> 00:30:57.265
Your body,

00:30:58.305 --> 00:30:59.785
everything that belongs to you,

00:30:59.865 --> 00:31:01.545
should belong to us too.

00:31:01.625 --> 00:31:02.705
Oh?

00:31:03.585 --> 00:31:05.545
Didn't everyone support the idea that

00:31:06.065 --> 00:31:10.505
my body belongs to me?

00:31:14.865 --> 00:31:16.265
It's your body,

00:31:17.545 --> 00:31:19.185
but it's my money.

00:31:28.305 --> 00:31:30.425
Then what should we do to make it fair?

00:31:33.225 --> 00:31:36.025
Should I divide myself
into pieces for everyone?

00:31:40.305 --> 00:31:41.625
Then come and take it.

00:32:03.945 --> 00:32:07.505
My body, my choice, Blossom.

00:32:40.825 --> 00:32:42.985
Welcome back to my channel.

00:32:45.985 --> 00:32:47.505
Just like I said,

00:32:50.785 --> 00:32:55.025
our bodies belong to us.

00:32:57.745 --> 00:32:58.825
So…

00:34:02.505 --> 00:34:05.145
We have to stop the opening
of the Hundred-Year Building.

00:34:05.865 --> 00:34:08.305
Your group wants to expose
the building corruption, right?

00:34:08.385 --> 00:34:09.665
I'll help you.

00:34:12.305 --> 00:34:14.705
Nanno, whose side are you really on?

00:34:16.585 --> 00:34:19.105
Don't disappoint me.

00:34:20.665 --> 00:34:21.825
Shit.

00:34:26.185 --> 00:34:28.905
If the Exclamation group
releases this clip,

00:34:28.985 --> 00:34:30.985
they're dead.

00:34:33.865 --> 00:34:35.545
The Exclamation group
still hasn't given up?

00:34:36.145 --> 00:34:37.465
Hide the truth.

00:34:38.785 --> 00:34:40.545
-Shit.
-Distract.

00:34:41.545 --> 00:34:44.065
That's the art
of those who control the game.

00:34:44.145 --> 00:34:45.345
Checkmate.

00:34:47.905 --> 00:34:49.745
This time,
they're definitely going to die.

00:36:44.465 --> 00:36:49.465
Subtitle translation by: Panuwat Baikeawon